                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message">
                            <div>Hello lbertran,</div><div><br /></div><div>Let's try hard reset.</div><div>Make sure the tv is ON, Do a hard reset.</div><div>1. Turn it off, and unplug it from the power outlet.</div><div>2. While the unit is turned off, look for the power button on the unit itself, press and hold it for about 15 seconds.&nbsp;</div><div>3. Unplug all devices connected at the back of the unit. Let the TV rest for about 1 minute, then turn on again</div><div><br /></div><div>Thank you.</div>                        </div>
